text = "[center]Site Echo 7 contains:

- Stylized first-person shooter combat
- Zombie violence (humanoid enemies)
- Mild horror imagery — dim lighting, alarms, screen-shake on damage
- No real-world military, pharma, or corporate branding
- No gore by default. A separate \"Gore Effects\" toggle in
  Settings enables blood burst particles on hit.
- Procedural audio only — no music, no voice acting

This is a single-player browser game. No data is sent
anywhere. Saves live in your browser's IndexedDB.

Press ACKNOWLEDGE to continue.[/center]"

